title: Gothic Americana
description:
For my first Torrent, I bring you some of my favorite obscure artists. These are what has been labelled Alt Country or Goth Americana, but I think of it as great music that is underappreciated in the Land of Popstars and Good Ol' Boys. enjoy!

16 Horsepower - 16 Horsepower, Sackcloth 'n' Ashes, Folklore, Hoarse, Low Estate, Olden, Secret South

Slim Cessna's Auto Club - Slim Cessna's Auto Club, Cipher, Always Say Please & Thank You, Crossbreeding Begins at Home

Jay Munly - Munly & the Lee Lewis Harlots

Reverend Glasseye - Our Lady of the Broken Spine

Tarentella - Esqueletos

Woven Hand - Woven Hand, Blush Music, Mosaic, Ten Stones, Consider The Birds
